API :
****
    *   Application Prohram Interface
    *   APIS's are everywhere
    *   Contract provided by one piece of software to another
    *   structure request and response .


REST API :
**********

REST  - Representational State Transfer .
API   - Application Programming Interface .
Rules :
*******

    *   create
    *   read
    *   update
    *   delete

eg :
    *   mobile application softwares .



Understanding REST API Methods :
********************************

REST provides a block of php methods which are used to alter the data .

the common HTTP methods are :
*****************************

    GET    : used for reading and retrieving data .
    POST   :  used for inserting data .
    PUT    :  used for updating data .
    DELETE : used for deleting data . 
    HEAD , OPTIONS , PATCH



*   any action URL is invoked , it perfroms an individual methods on that URL .


(web application)         (API)              (server) 
CUSTOMERS       ------------------------->   KITCHEN
                <-------------------------



header('Content-Type : application/json');
    * application return in json format .

header('Access-Control-Allow-Methods : PUT');

header('Access-Control-Allow-Origin : *');

header('Access-Control-Allow-Headers : <header-name>');







